Package: mongolstats
Type: Package
Title: Mongolian NSO Open Data and Boundaries (Tidy Client)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Temuulen",
             family = "",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "temuulen@gmail.com"))
Description: A tidyverse-friendly client for the National Statistics Office of Mongolia
    Open Data API (opendata.1212.mn) with helpers to discover tables, variables, and fetch
    statistical data. Also includes utilities to retrieve Mongolia administrative boundaries
    (ADM0-ADM2) as 'sf' objects from open sources for mapping and spatial analysis.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    sf,
    rlang,
    memoise,
    cachem,
    rappdirs,
    stringi,
    stringdist
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    pkgdown
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
